---
title: Smart Double Turkey Meatball and Veggie Soup with Buttered Toasts
description: Tender turkey meatballs made with breadcrumbs and Italian seasoning are paired with a medley of veggies in a marinara broth to make this light but nourishing soup. This cozy bowl of deliciousness will have everyone saying, "mmmm...good soup!"
